{"tid":1125983,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"哥帥入場見證 利記挫曼城捧英足盃","createTime":"2019-04-26T05:24:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T06:17:00.000Z","uid":186071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f0fd30a31b0d7b969bdc95f1fb204fc45e7967fc","tid":1125983,"uid":186071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T05:24:18.000Z","msg":"Now Sports-體育】利物浦壓倒曼城！說的不是英超，而是英格蘭青年足總盃決賽。利物浦U18周四對曼城U18，雙方激戰120分鐘後打成1:1平手，最終利物浦在曼城一隊主帥哥迪奧拿見證下，互射12碼贏5:3，其中謝拉特的表弟更妙射得手。<br />\n這場U18盃賽，兩隊戰力不相上下，曼城由杜亞斯率先打破僵局，為曼城領先1:0。到了比賽的尾聲，利物浦球員卜比鄧肯（Bobby Duncan，謝拉特的表弟）射入一記世界波，為球隊扳平比數進入加時。雙方在加時中再無入球，比賽亦進入12碼大戰。 互射12碼時，曼城第2名主射球員射中門楣，而利物浦5名球員全部射入，最終12碼大戰，利物浦U18贏5:3，總比數6:4擊敗曼城U18，奪得今季青年足總盃的冠軍。這也是自2007年以來，利物浦事隔12年再捧這座獎盃。 曼城主帥哥迪奧拿是今仗的座上客，看見小將被利物浦所敗，相信亦會感到失望。<br />\n<a href=\"http://更多now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%9Anow.com&d=fAF%2FER2cs4qp%2F6NYk0BreGzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=ded20264\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">更多now.com</a>體育新聞及英超、西甲精華，請按此<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/67920382572/posts/10157837177092573?sfns=xmo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F67920382572%2Fposts%2F10157837177092573%3Fsfns%3Dxmo&d=fAF%2FER2cs4qp%2F6NYk0BreGzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=65476d1c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/67920382572/posts/10157837177092573?sfns=xmo</a>"},{"pid":"ed2191ab34f8478a4f63f5cbe6b0fb6306c107bf","tid":1125983,"uid":29820,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T05:40:12.000Z","msg":"利物浦壓倒曼城！說的不是英超<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c07d3305f4ef12f9bb4892870de788c11cadcd9e","tid":1125983,"uid":178619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T05:42:49.000Z","msg"